
Darknet pioneers and representatives from the movie and music industries square off over the new realities of digital distribution over private spaces online. Kori Bernards (MPAA), Heather Champ (Flickr), Ian Clarke (Freenet), Mark Ishikawa (BayTSP), JD Lasica (Darknet), and Dave Toole (Outhink) participate.

